entities.name: arithmetic-combinator
entities.player_description:
Calculate the average number of items per chest.
Using only the first car because a short-train could leave it empty while later cars make the station think it has capacity.

entities.name: selector-combinator
entities.player_description: This outputs a 1 signal for something to be loaded in the rocket. If there are full rockets of a particular item to be sent, it'll output one of those. If not, it'll output one of the remaining components.
